Class AtomTypeLeaf

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.atom.AtomTypeLeaf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IAtomType, java.lang.Comparable<IAtomType>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AtomTypeOrientedSphere, AtomTypeSpheroPolyhedron

    public class AtomTypeLeaf
extends java.lang.Object
implements IAtomType, java.lang.Comparable<IAtomType>
    Type for an atom that is a leaf in the species hierarchy. An atom of this type is typically representing a physical atom, rather than a group of other atoms.
